      "releaseNotes": "1. New Feature: Added support for exporting fonts in \"Vertical Layout\" format, which can be enabled in the preview settings.\n2. New Feature: Internationalization support. The app interface now supports Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, and English.\n3. New Feature: Added format detection for imported external fonts. A pop-up will appear if the format is incorrect.\n4. Bug Fix: Fixed an issue where fonts generated while running the iPadOS app on macOS could not be exported.\n5. Bug Fix: Improved the instructional text on some interface screens.",
      "version": "1.2",
